The evidence with the title 'Robert Hurt (politician) - Wikipedia ' says Robert Hurt (born june 16, 1969) is an American politician who served as the U.S. representative for Virginia 's 5th congressional district from 2011 to 2017.  ... Hurt voted two dozen times to cut taxes and supported 28 bills in the General Assembly  ... Hurt was elected to the Senate of Virginia , winning 75 percent of the vote . 
